vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; float: left; width: 319.703px;\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 0; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 319.703px; height: 228.047px; background-color: rgb(217, 91, 67); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://betado.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2016/12/15681688_10154826703653088_1352202168_o.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox[25020]\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(217, 91, 67); display: block; width: 319.703px; height: 228.047px; outline: 0px !important;\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"214\" src=\"https://betado.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2016/12/15681688_10154826703653088_1352202168_o-300x214.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium\" alt=\"15681688_10154826703653088_1352202168_o\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 319.703px; transition: opacity 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.25, 0.75, 0.75);\"></a></dt></dl><dl class=\"gallery-item\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; float: left; width: 319.703px;\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 0; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 319.703px; height: 228.047px; background-color: rgb(217, 91, 67); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://betado.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2016/12/15682139_10154826703648088_1079410278_o.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox[25020]\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(217, 91, 67); display: block; width: 319.703px; height: 228.047px; outline: 0px !important;\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"214\" src=\"https://betado.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2016/12/15682139_10154826703648088_1079410278_o-300x214.jpg\" class=\"attachment-medium\" alt=\"15682139_10154826703648088_1079410278_o\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 319.703px; transition: opacity 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.25, 0.75, 0.75);\"></a></dt></dl><br style=\"clear: both;\"><br style=\"clear: both;\"></div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.2rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\">The playground is designed by Think Playgrounds and includes a tree house, a set of railway and a set of wood games for the children to climb so that they can be more active and creative. The playground will turn each break time into an adventure in the woods or an voyage to the new land. It is built with environmentally-friendly materials such as car tires or eucalyptus wood. With three years of experience in designing and constructing community playgrounds, the professional team has come up with the solution to make the playground more durable.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.2rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\">Nowadays, many residents of the island still lead a free and nomadic life, so they don’t have the habit of using the toilet properly. In order to raise the children’s awareness in protecting the environment and protecting their health, we hope to build a spacious and modern restroom.</p><h1 style=\"margin-top: 2.4rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 3rem; line-height: 3.8rem; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\">OUR TARGET:</h1><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.2rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\">To implement the project, we hope to raise 170 million VND to build a playground and a restroom for children on Hon Chuoi Island. The money will be used as follows:</p><ol style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\"><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 600; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">60 million VND</span>&nbsp;– Build a new restroom for the students and children on the island</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 600; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">90 million VND</span>&nbsp;– Build a new playground for the children</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 600; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">20 million VND</span>&nbsp;– The operational, transportation, construction expenses …</li></ol><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\"><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Duration: From 23 Dec 2016 to 13 Jan 2017</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Construction period at the workshop of Think Playgrounds: From 09 Jan to 23 Jan 2017</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Install the playground on Hon Chuoi Island: From 12 Feb to 19 Feb 2017</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Issue the report on the project, publicize the financial details and send the video clip of the implementation period to the backers: 28 Feb 2017</li></ul><h1 style=\"margin-top: 2.4rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 3rem; line-height: 3.8rem; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\">PROJECT AGENCIES</h1><h2 style=\"margin: 2.4rem 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 2.5rem; line-height: 3.4rem; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\">ORGANIZING AGENCY – Humans of Hà Nội</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.2rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/humansofhanoi/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(217, 91, 67); outline: 0px !important;\">https://www.facebook.com/humansofhanoi/</a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.2rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\"><a href=\"https://betado.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2016/12/HOHN-logo.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox[25020]\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(217, 91, 67); outline: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-25087\" src=\"https://betado.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2016/12/HOHN-logo-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"HOHN logo\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem 1rem; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; height: auto; float: right;\"></a>Humans of Hà Nội, a community project founded on 1st Dec 2013, is the place where the ordinary moments of the life and people who are living, working in, or just passing by Hanoi are preserved.<br>Currently, Humans of Hà Nội has a store of 1000 stories about Hanoians by means of photos and videos. Besides, Humans of Hanoi is one of an impactful community projects receiving a lot of support from the community.</p><h2 style=\"margin: 2.4rem 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 2.5rem; line-height: 3.4rem; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\">CONSTRUCTION AGENCY – Think Playgrounds</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.2rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\"><a href=\"http://sanchoi.org/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(217, 91, 67); outline: 0px !important;\">http://sanchoi.org</a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.2rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\"><a href=\"https://betado.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2016/12/Think-playgrounds.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox[25020]\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(217, 91, 67); outline: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"alignright size-thumbnail wp-image-25086\" src=\"https://betado.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2016/12/Think-playgrounds-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"Think playgrounds\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem 1rem; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; height: auto; float: right;\"></a>Think Playgrounds is an organization founded with a view to finding the efficient and creative solutions to build the playgrounds for children. After almost 3 years of operation, the team has built more than 30 playgrounds for children in Hanoi and other remote areas.<br>Think Playgrounds has collaborated with the residential areas to create a public space for the children and worked with the creative architects to build an appropriate design and use the recycled materials to make the toys, which are both economical and durable.</p><div id=\"attachment_25034\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"margin: 1.2rem auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; clear: both; text-align: center; color: rgb(125, 110, 99); width: 1034px;\"><a href=\"https://betado.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2016/12/05.-San-choi-bai-giu%CC%9B%CC%83a-.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox[25020]\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(217, 91, 67); outline: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-25034\" src=\"https://betado.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2016/12/05.-San-choi-bai-giu%CC%9B%CC%83a-.jpg\" alt=\"Sân chơi ở bãi giữa sông hồng Hà Nội. ( 2014 )\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; height: auto; position: relative;\"></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2rem; padding: 0px 1rem; border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.1rem; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline-block;\">Sân chơi ở bãi giữa sông hồng Hà Nội. ( 2014 )</p></div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.2rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\">&nbsp;</p><div id=\"attachment_25035\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\" style=\"margin: 1.2rem auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; clear: both; text-align: center; color: rgb(125, 110, 99); width: 970px;\"><a href=\"https://betado.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2016/12/06.-San-choi-bai-giu%CC%9B%CC%83a-.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox[25020]\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(217, 91, 67); outline: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-25035\" src=\"https://betado.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2016/12/06.-San-choi-bai-giu%CC%9B%CC%83a-.jpg\" alt=\"Sân chơi trường tiểu học và mấu giáo Suối Lìn, Vân Hồ, Sơn La. ( 2015 )\" width=\"960\" height=\"637\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; height: auto; position: relative;\"></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\" style=\"margin-bottom: 1.2rem; padding: 0px 1rem; border: 0px; font-style: italic; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.1rem; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; display: inline-block;\">Sân chơi trường tiểu học và mấu giáo Suối Lìn, Vân Hồ, Sơn La. ( 2015 )</p></div><h2 style=\"margin: 2.4rem 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 2.5rem; line-height: 3.4rem; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\">Đơn vị bảo trợ truyền thông:</h2><h2 style=\"margin: 2.4rem 0px 1.2rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 2.5rem; line-height: 3.4rem; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\">Kenh14.vn</h2><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.2rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\"><a href=\"http://kenh14.vn/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(217, 91, 67); outline: 0px !important;\">http://www.kenh14.vn</a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.2rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\"><a href=\"https://betado.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2016/12/15657918_1071256302997216_1556898299_o.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox[25020]\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(217, 91, 67); outline: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"alignright wp-image-25085 size-thumbnail\" src=\"https://betado.com/wp-content/uploads/edd/2016/12/15657918_1071256302997216_1556898299_o-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"15657918_1071256302997216_1556898299_o\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.2rem 1rem; padding: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 100%; height: auto; float: right;\"></a>Kenh14.vn, owned by VCCorp, has now been the biggest website of social lifestyle and entertainment information in Vietnam. With serious investment in the content, human resources as well as the up-to-date trends in every aspect of life, Kenh14.vn is getting better day by day and deserves to be the reliable channel of information for the youth and the entire community as well!<br>The touching story of Mr. Tran Binh Phuc and his students on Hon Chuoi Island has been revealed in the WeChoice Awards 2016 – an award which celebrates the impactful sources of inspiration to spread them to our society, wake up the belief, happiness and love among human beings.</p><h1 style=\"margin-top: 2.4rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 3rem; line-height: 3.8rem; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\">Payment method:</h1><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.2rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\">The following payment methods are supported:</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\"><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Internet Banking or domestic ATM card or credit card</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Paypal</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Direct transfer at the local bank (For those who don’t have a bank account)</li></ul><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 1.2rem; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\">For further assistance regarding payment, please contact the hotline: 0949 401851</p><h1 style=\"margin-top: 2.4rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 3rem; line-height: 3.8rem; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\">CONTACT US</h1><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, Times, serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(125, 110, 99);\"><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Mobile: 094 358 1993 (Mr. Hoàng Long)</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Email: humansofhanoi@gmail.com</li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0.6rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Facebook:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/humansofhanoi\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(217, 91, 67); outline: 0px !important;\">https://www.facebook.com/humansofhanoi</a></li><li></li></ul></div></div>', '8579.jpg', 'đảo Hòn Chuối', 15, NULL, 60, '2018-05-07 11:32:15', '2018-07-06 11:19:54', 1, 22735, 0, '2018-05-07 11:19:54', '2018-05-07 16:55:42');
INSERT INTO `campaigns` (`id`, `user_id`, `title`, `goal`, `tagline`, `pitch`, `avatar`, `location`, `category_id`, `priority`, `duration`, `start_at`, `end_at`, `status`, `exchange_rate`, `delete_flag`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(2057, 1002, 'Bad Luck', 10000000, 'Bad Luck la một Series truyện tranh hài hước 4 khung do tác giả Nguyễn Huỳnh Bảo Châu ( còn được biết đến với tên gọi: Châu Chặt Chém) sáng tác.  Bộ truyện được phát hành miễn phí trên mạng thông qua Page Facebook của tác giả từ tháng 4/2015. và được đông đảo người đọc ủng hộ', '<h1 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Bad Luck là gì?</h1><p style=\"margin-top: -0.5em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Bad Luck la một Series&nbsp;truyện tranh hài hước 4 khung do tác giả Nguyễn Huỳnh Bảo Châu ( còn được biết đến với tên gọi: Châu Chặt Chém) sáng tác.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Bộ truyện được phát hành miễn phí trên mạng thông qua Page Facebook của tác giả từ tháng 4/2015. và được đông đảo người đọc ủng hộ, yêu quý</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Các bạn có thể đọc truyện Bad Luck tại đây:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BadLuckComic\" style=\"outline: none; color: rgb(94, 165, 215); line-height: inherit;\">https://www.facebook.com/BadLuckComic</a></p><h1 style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: Roboto, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.5em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Sự cuồng nhiệt của Bad Luck</h1><p style=\"margin-top: -0.5em; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Ngay từ những trang đầu tiên,Bad Luck nhanh chóng tạo ra được một cơn sốt vô cùng khủng khiếp bởi sự hài hước trong cốt truyện, sự sáng tạo đột phá trong tính cách nhân vật và gây shock về tình tiết. Chỉ trong một thời gian rất ngắn Badluck đã là món ăn tinh thần không thể thiếu với rất nhiều độc giả ủng hộ bộ truyện này.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Cộng đồng fan hâm mộ Bad Luck với hơn 4 ngàn người tham gia trong vòng vài ngày tại địa chỉ:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/BadLuckComic/\" style=\"outline: none; color: rgb(94, 165, 215); line-height: inherit;\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/BadLuckComic/</a></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Một số fanart do độc giả vẽ tặng bộ truyện:</p><div id=\"gallery-1\" class=\"gallery galleryid-52697 gallery-columns-4 gallery-size-thumbnail\" style=\"margin: auto; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><dl class=\"gallery-item\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; position: relative; float: left; text-align: center; width: 285px;\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\" style=\"margin: 0px 10px 0px 0px; padding: 3px; direction: ltr; position: relative; overflow: hidden; max-width: 100%; border: 1px solid rgb(225, 225, 225); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15) 0px 0px 8px;\"><a href=\"http://comicola.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/11701135_833324443447775_5540352398995393931_n.jpg\" title=\"\" rel=\"lig