 228px;\"><dt class=\"gallery-icon landscape\" style=\"margin: 0px 10px 0px 0px; padding: 3px; direction: ltr; position: relative; overflow: hidden; max-width: 100%; border: 1px solid rgb(225, 225, 225); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15) 0px 0px 8px;\"><a href=\"http://comicola.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/vantich_wip1.jpg\" title=\"\" rel=\"lightbox[gallery-1]\" data-lightbox-gallery=\"lightbox[gallery-1]\" style=\"outline: none; color: rgb(94, 165, 215); line-height: inherit;\"><img width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"http://comicola.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/vantich_wip1-200x200.jpg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"vantich_wip1\" srcset=\"http://comicola.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/vantich_wip1-200x200.jpg 200w, http://comicola.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/vantich_wip1-300x300.jpg 300w, http://comicola.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/vantich_wip1-500x500.jpg 500w, http://comicola.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/vantich_wip1-32x32.jpg 32w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-width: 2px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(207, 207, 207); display: block; width: 210px;\"></a></dt></dl><br style=\"clear: both;\"></div><p style=\"margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; direction: ltr; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: inherit; color: rgb(85, 85, 85);\">Nếu gây quỹ thành công &nbsp;lần này với số tiền 100 triệu, chúng tôi sẽ dùng số tiền ấy để:</p><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 17px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1em; direction: ltr; list-style-position: inside; line-height: 1.6; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent: -1em;\"><li style=\"margin: 0px